[size=3]install[/size]

DONE![/size]

[size=3][size=3]for racemenu users just install with your favorite mods manager[/size], in game choose Nord race and load the preset named kristen stewart or nathalie portman
[/size][size=3]DONE![/size]

[color=#ffff00][size=3]for ece users:
it may be that this does not give the same result with your skyrim, depending on the mods you
have installed, an example: if you have more hair/eyes mods installed,
when you would load the preset it will not necessarily the same
hair/eyes.[/size][/color][size=3][color=#ffff00]
[/color]
[/size][color=#e06666][size=3]also other textures and ENB can alter the appearance, you are warned  ;)[/size][/color][color=#e06666]
you don't like air, eyes color, shape.., just change it yourself ;)
[size=5]remember that it's a preset so you can edit it at your convenience!![/size][/color]
